[13:09] <brrt> if it uses e.g. 2 bytes rather than 1 byte for the 'jmp' offset, any labels after it move, as well
[13:10] <brrt> the usual solution is to be pessimistic about how much space you'll need, and decrement if you need less
[13:10] <brrt> but somehow, that's not applied correctly here
